Package com.telenav.kivakit.ui.desktop.graphics.drawing.geometry

Class DrawingObject

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.ui.desktop.graphics.drawing.geometry.DrawingObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Coordinated
Direct Known Subclasses:
DrawingLength, DrawingLine, DrawingPoint, DrawingRectangle, DrawingSize
public abstract class DrawingObject extends Object implements Coordinated
An object in a CoordinateSystem. The normalized() methods convert geometric objects from their coordinate system to the coordinate system for this object.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
